Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:46.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}找来了各种不请自来的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:49.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}也算是某种因果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:51.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}如果放弃 干脆不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:54.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}也就省了这档子事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}总觉得不爽
