Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}或者根本不要见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:09.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}不管说明书上怎么写
